title: The Gray Havens
desc: Husband-wife Dave and Licia Radford comprise ?The Gray Havens , a folk-pop duo whose unique artistry draws from such influences as C.S. Lewis, JRR Tolkien, and Jonathan Edwards. ?Their debut full-length recording,? Fire and Stone ,? is being hailed as ?a phenomenal recording,? and reached the Top 10 on national mainstream Singer-Songwriter charts.
